      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The exterior has significant rust along the wheel wells and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy staining and tears in the upholstery. Mechanically, the engine is functional but suffers from a persistent oil leak and a rough idle, and the transmission occasionally slips. This car will require substantial mechanical and cosmetic work to be roadworthy.",
